  # OpenAccess Providers
  
  Per-provider folders (STC, ITC, ACES, DOWIYAT). Each provider contains
  journey subfolders from Activation through Termination, plus
  Installation-Failure, Cancel-Order, and Mesh-Extender-Standalone where
  applicable.
  
  Shared OA service-order and TMF641/SingleView steps: `Shared-Workflows/`.
}

